title: Have you seen it? Home in Tacoma. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Gorgeously Remodeled Rambler in central Tacoma location.
This One story home offers an open concept living, w/ Luxury Vinyl Planks Throughout the whole house.
The Kitchen has all new cabinets, Quarts counter tops, w/ backsplash, stainless steel appliances and an  island with eat in area.
Living room has lots of natural daylight entering into the room w/ tiled fireplace.
Mater suite has 3/4 private shower w/ walk in closet.
All new: millwork, door, trim, new toilets, new fixtures, windows, garage door, exterior and interior paint and so much more.
The lot is Huge with lots of parking for toys, boats or RV's.
Close to freeway, military bases and shopping areas
